title: 1992–93 Eastern Counties Football League
text:
The 1992–93 Eastern Counties Football League season was the 51st in the history of <a href="Eastern%20Counties%20Football%20League">Eastern Counties Football League</a> a <a href="association%20football">football</a> competition in England.
